title: [Epidemiology] Adults with positive SARS-CoV-2 test results were approximately twice as likely to have reported dining at a restaurant than were those with negative SARS-CoV-2 test results

[Epidemiology] 12 young children acquired COVID-19 in child care facilities and transmitted it to at least 12 household members, with 1 parent hospitalized, including transmission from 2 of 3 children with asymptomatic COVID-19. (US CDC MMWR, 11 Sep 2020)
